Always import 'react' when we use html in our component.

three things importants to know:
Component - It's a function that returns a html whith or not CSS ans Javascript content. It's not recomended have two or more components in same file. In resume: It's a isolated block of HTML, CSS and JS which doesn't interfere in the application

Property - Information who father component pass to son component.

State - Information maintained by component (remember: Immutability)

